  "prompt": "What is the fee structure of Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam?",
  "response": "The fee structure at Sri Chaitanya Educational Institutions, including their Visakhapatnam branch, can vary depending on the specific program, course, and grade level you are interested in. Sri Chaitanya offers a range of educational programs, including school education (from kindergarten to 12th grade), intermediate, and coaching for competitive exams like IIT-JEE, NEET, and others.\n\n### General Fee Structure Guidelines:\n1. **School Programs (KG to 10th Grade):**  \n   Fees typically range from \u20b950,000 to \u20b91,50,000 per annum, depending on the grade and facilities provided.\n\n2. **Intermediate (11th and 12th Grade):**  \n   For MPC (Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry) or BiPC (Biology, Physics, Chemistry) streams, fees can range from \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b92,00,000 per annum.\n\n3. **Competitive Exam Coaching (IIT-JEE, NEET, etc.):**  \n   Fees for coaching programs can range from \u20b91,50,000 to \u20b93,00,000 per annum, depending on the course duration, study material, and facilities.\n\n4. **Boarding Facilities:**  \n   Additional charges for boarding and lodging may apply, typically ranging from \u20b950,000 to \u20b91,50,000 per annum, depending on the type of accommodation.\n\n### Important Notes:\n- The fees may vary based on the specific branch in Visakhapatnam, as different branches may have slightly different fee structures.\n- Sri Chaitanya often provides scholarships or discounts for meritorious students.\n- Fees may include tuition, study materials, uniforms, and examination fees, but additional costs for extra activities or trips may apply.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, it is recommended to contact the Visakhapatnam branch directly or visit their official website. You can also inquire about any ongoing offers or financial aid options.",
